 WWF Wrestling Challenge - 3/24/90

 It's a week before WrestleMania VI, and Tony Schiavone and Gorilla Monsoon bring you World Wrestling Federation action! This episode aired on 24th March 1990 (25th March in some markets) in the New York market. 

 The card is as follows: 

 Wrestling Challenge taping: 
 3/24/90 - included Gene Okerlund conducting an interview with Dusty Rhodes & Sapphire: 
 Brutus Beefcake pinned Steve Vega 
 Dino Bravo (w/ Jimmy Hart) defeated Ricki Ataki; after the bout, Ron Garvin made the save against Bravo and Jimmy Hart 
 Mr. Perfect defeated Dale Wolfe 
 Jake Roberts defeated Darryl Nichols 
 Akeem (w/ Slick) pinned Nito Gomez at 1:05 with the splash
